			<p class="lead">
				Where exactly and how much of the Internet traffic is scanned and saved by secret services
				is not entirely known (at July 4th, 2013). Our visualisation shows examples of how internet
				packets wander around the world's internet cables while we use some of the most popular
				internet services. Each country your data packets visit offers an opportunity for snooping.
				This NewsApp can be embedded
